features: PREMIUM STUDENT QUALITY CRAYONS FOR UNLEASHING YOUR CREATIVITY All bulk crayons are teacher approved quality, comparable to major brands at a budget friendly price, designed with high quality wax and fine sharpened tips offering smooth consistency great for your kids’ crayon coloring and creative drawings.

BEST BULK VALUE CRAYON PACK Imagine all the art and craft projects that you and your kids will color for days with 240 crayons. Enough to meet all your classroom needs, teacher supplies, school projects, home art supplies, party favors or gift bags. The cost-per-crayon is lower than most competitors.

BULK SET OF 10 VIBRANT CRAYONS Each 10 box bulk pack has an even assortment of 24 classic colors including red, red orange, orange, yellow orange, yellow, yellow green, green, green blue, aquamarine, sky blue, blue, cerulean, navy blue, violet, red violet, magenta, bubblegum, pink, lavender, peach, brown, black, gray and white.

CRAYONS ARE SAFE, DURABLE & STORAGE FRIENDLY All Color Swell Crayon Bulk Sets are nontoxic, conform to safety standards with sturdy individual boxes for easy storage. TEACHER LOVED crayons for home art projects, class packs, and students with trusted durability.

While Color Swell crayons are perfect for all types of uses – especially coloring and drawing – they were not specifically designed for melting. Color Swell crayons may be used for melting but the wrappers may be difficult to remove for some users.
The Color Swell mission is to donate bulk colored pencils and other art supplies to kids in need for every product sold, we couldn’t do this without PHENOMENAL CUSTOMER SERVICE!
